{"type":"message","id":"11d51c40","parentId":"04180104","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:47:27.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a Frontend Developer specializing in React/Next.js. However, they haven't given me a specific task yet - they've just set up the context for what I am.\n\nI should acknowledge this role and ask what specific frontend development task they need help with.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"สวัสดีครับ! 🐣✨\n\nรับทราบครับ ผมพร้อมทำหน้าที่เป็น Frontend Developer สำหรับโปรเจกต์ React/Next.js\n\n**Frontend Stack ที่ผมถนัด:**\n- **Framework:** Next.js 14+ (App Router), React 18+\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS, CSS Modules, Styled Components\n- **State Management:** Zustand, React Query/TanStack Query, Context API\n- **UI Libraries:** shadcn/ui, Radix UI, Headless UI\n- **Forms:** React Hook Form + Zod\n- **Animations:** Framer Motion, CSS transitions\n- **Performance:** Lazy loading, code splitting, image optimization\n\n**บริการที่พร้อมให้:**\n1. 🎨 สร้าง UI Components (responsive, accessible)\n2. ⚡ จัดการ State & Data Fetching\n3. 🔗 API Integration (REST/GraphQL)\n4. 📱 Responsive Design (mobile-first)\n5. 🚀 Performance Optimization\n\n**มีงานอะไรให้ผมช่วยครับ?** \nเช่น:\n- สร้าง component/page ใหม่\n- Refactor โค้ดเก่า\n- ตั้งค่า project structure\n- แก้บั๊ก UI\n- อื่นๆ..."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":7757,"output":386,"cacheRead":2816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772088441597}}
